  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li>New Drag &amp; Drop Panel Widget : SplitterBox</li><li>Either horizontal or vertical flow</li><li>Let users at runtime resize children by moving the separator between children with the mouse</li><li>Set the size with classic AUTO vs FILL</li><li>Minimum size in pixels for children.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Code Modules:</p><ul><li>Â UMG_Splitter (Runtime)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprints: 0</p><p>Number of C&#43;&#43; Classes: 3</p><p>Network Replicated: No</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: Windows, Mac, Linux</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms: Win32, Win64, Mac, Linux, IOS, Android</p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JaUiYqjHf-4Vaj81IpozVHzSQ7bNMGNXlFNPDjA334Y/edit?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JaUiYqjHf-4Vaj81IpozVHzSQ7bNMGNXlFNPDjA334Y/edit?usp&#61;sharing</a></p><p>Example Project: https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fo/qe8p5717nwiehcoilfvg3/h?rlkey&#61;shrk3hzjavv11g1fj93357a9n&amp;dl&#61;0</p>",
